# File Encode and Decode utils

- Requires 0.0.123 version of the plugin
    - sfdx-mohanc-plugins@0.0.123
    - [How to install the plugin](https://mohan-chinnappan-n.github.io/dx/plugins.html#/1)


## Topics
- [Encode a given binary file using base64](#encode)
- [decode a given base64 encoded file ](#decode)

<a name="encode"></a>
## Encode

- Encoding a zip file
```

$ jar tvf /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip
 38702 Thu Nov 19 19:13:30 EST 2020 unpackaged/siteDotComSites/selfservice1.site
   192 Thu Nov 19 19:13:30 EST 2020 unpackaged/siteDotComSites/selfservice1.site-meta.xml
   222 Thu Nov 19 19:13:30 EST 2020 unpackaged/package.xml

```

```
$ sfdx mohanc:data:file:encode -d /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip 
=== Given file /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip is of mime type: application/zip.
=== Base64 encoded content of the file /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip will be written to /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip.txt ...

```
<a name="decode"></a>

## Decode

- decoding a base64 encoded zip file content
```
$ cat /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip.txt

```
- 
```
$ sfdx mohanc:data:file:decode -d /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip.txt 
=== Base64 decoded content of the file /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip.txt will be written to /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip.txt.dec ...
=== Writing  decoded file content to /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip.txt.dec ... 
```
- Checking the decoded zip file 
```
$ jar -tvf /tmp/09S3h000005TvdiEAC.zip.txt.dec 
 38702 Thu Nov 19 19:13:30 EST 2020 unpackaged/siteDotComSites/selfservice1.site
   192 Thu Nov 19 19:13:30 EST 2020 unpackaged/siteDotComSites/selfservice1.site-meta.xml
   222 Thu Nov 19 19:13:30 EST 2020 unpackaged/package.xml
```
